Q1)

REM program to generate 2,2,4,6,10 upto 10th term.
DECLARE SUB FIBO()
CLS
EXECUTE FIBO
END
SUB FIBO
A=2
B=2
FOR Ctr=5 to 1
DISPLAY A;B;
A=A+B
B=A+B
NEXT Ctr
END FUNCTION
Solution:

DECLARE SUB FIBO()
CLS
CALL FIBO
END
SUB FIBO
A=2
B=2
FOR Ctr=5 to 1 STEP -1
PRINT A;B;
A=A+B
B=A+B
NEXT Ctr
END SUB
